course_description: The second course in a 3-course series prepares the student to conceptualize and develop a site-specific project plan in collaboration with a sponsoring facility, site and/or Clinical Partner. Students learn the steps to project development/management, and negotiation skills to conduct the project.
prerequisites: NRSG 715D or equivalent transfer credit as prerequisite.
